     D TRANSDTL        S           5800A
     D PSTS            S             24A
     D PDealNumber     S              6A
     D PActCode        S              1A                                                      CIR008
     D PRTCD           S              7A                                                      CIR008
     D POPTN           S              7A                                                      CIR008
